NATURAL FLAVORS, POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE), LACTIC ACID, PARIKA EXTRACT (CANOLA OIL, NATURAL EXTRACTIVES OF PAPRIKA, NATURAL FLAVORS, ASCORBIC ACID), AND NOT MORE THAN 2% SILICON DIOXIDE TO AID PROCESSING), CHEDDAR CHEESE INGREDIENT (CHEDDAR CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES), WATER, SODIUM PHOSPHATE), WHITE DISTILLED VINEGAR, NATURAL CHEESE FLAVOR (INCLUDING BLUE CHEESE), WATER, SALT, DISODIUM PHOSPHATE AND XANTHAN GUM)).

Shredded Monterey Jack Cheese: Monterey Jack Cheese (Pasteurized Milk, Cheese Culture, Salt, Enzymes), Cheddar Cheese (Pasteurized Milk, Cheese Culture, Salt, Enzymes, Annatto), Potato Starch, Powdered Cellulose (Anti-Caking Agent), Natamycin (A Natural Mold Inhibitor)..

Parmesan Cheese: IMITATION PARMESAN CHEESE (WATER, FOOD STARCH, CASEINATE, NATURAL FLAVOR, PALM OIL, MILKFAT, SALT, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE, LACTIC ACID, SORBIC ACID (AS A PRESERVATIVE), ARTIFICIAL COLOR), POWDERED CELLULOSE (ANTI-CAKING AGENT).

BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR ENRICHED ((BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), MALTED BARLEY FLOUR), WATER, WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, GRAIN MIX (HARD RED WHEAT, OAT GROATS, TRITICALE, BARLEY, RYE, SOFT WHITE WHEAT, SPELT, HARD WHITE WHEAT, FLAX SEED), WHOLE GRAIN BARLEY, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF SOYBEAN OIL, SALT, YELLOW PRUSSIATE OF SODA, YEAST, MALTED BARLEY, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, BROWN SUGAR, YELLOW CORNMEAL, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), EXTENDER (WHEAT FLOUR, ENZYMES, SALT), NATURAL BEER TYPE FLAVOR (DEXTROSE, MALTODEXTRIN, NATURAL FLAVORS, SILICON DIOXIDE (ANTI-CAKING AGENT), SALT), COCOA (PROCESSED WITH ALKALI), DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), MALT POWDER (MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, DEXTROSE, WHEAT FLOUR).

ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR [WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID], WATER, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: SOYBEAN AND/OR CANOLA OIL, YEAST, SALT, SUGAR, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, CALCIUM SULFATE, ACACIA GUM, MONO- & DIGLYCERIDES, ENZYMES), BAKING POWDER (SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, SODIUM BICARBONATE, CORNSTARCH, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE), NONFAT DRY MILK, PRESERVATIVES (CALCIUM PROPIONATE, POTASSIUM SORBATE, CALCIUM ACETATE), YEAST NUTRIENTS (CALCIUM SULFATE, AMMONIUM SULFATE, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES).

ENRICHED BLEACHED FLOUR (BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, SUGAR, YEAST, SOYBEAN OIL, IODIZED SALT (SALT, SODIUM SILICOALUMINATE, DEXTROSE, POTASSIUM IODIDE), SPONGE EXTRACT (WATER, FERMENTED WHEAT FLOUR), VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, ITALIAN SEASONING (MARJORAM, THYME, ROSEMARY, SAVORY, SAGE, OREGANO, BASIL), DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES).

WATER, WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR ENRICHED ((BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), MALTED BARLEY FLOUR), HONEY, SOYBEAN OIL, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: YEAST, SALT, YELLOW PRUSSIATE OF SODA, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), EXTENDER (WHEAT FLOUR, ENZYMES, SALT), MALT POWDER (MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, DEXTROSE, WHEAT FLOUR), DRY MILK SOLIDS (WHEY POWDER, NONFAT DRY MILK).

WATER, ENRICHED BLEACHED FLOUR (BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, MIXED GRAINS (RYE FLAKES, ROLLED WHEAT, ROLLED OATS, MILLET, FLAX SEEDS, SESAME SEEDS), BLACKSTRAP MOLASSES, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, CHICORY INULIN, IODIZED SALT (SALT, SODIUM SILICOALUMINATE, DEXTROSE, POTASSIUM IODIDE), SOYBEAN OIL, YEAST, SPONGE EXTRACT (WATER, FERMENTED WHEAT FLOUR), CARAMEL COLOR, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES).

BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR ENRICHED ((BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), MALTED BARLEY FLOUR), WATER, SALTED BUTTER (PASTEURIZED CREAM, SALT), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: YEAST, SALT, YELLOW PRUSSIATE OF SODA, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, SUGAR, EXTENDER (WHEAT FLOUR, ENZYMES, SALT), DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ENZYMES), SODIUM HYDROXIDE.

(BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR ENRICHED ((BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), MALTED BARLEY FLOUR), WATER, WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, SOYBEAN OIL, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: SALT, YELLOW PRUSSIATE OF SODA, YEAST, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, SUGAR, NONFAT DRY MILK, WHEY SOLIDS, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, INACTIVE DRIED YEAST, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), MALT POWDER (MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, DEXTROSE, WHEAT FLOUR), EXTENDER (WHEAT FLOUR, ENZYMES, SALT))
